title: Hour 1 - Darren Rovell (03-31-20)

description:
Jason Smith and Rob Parker fill in for Dan Patrick and react to the good news that was finally delivered to the sports world! The guys debate whether or not the NBA season will get cancelled and predict how the Patriots will fare without Tom Brady
